      {
        "step_no": 1,
        "text": "Make toasted rice powder: toast the uncooked rice in a dry skillet over medium heat, stirring frequently, until golden and nutty (watch carefully), then transfer to a mortar and pestle or spice grinder and grind to a coarse powder.",
